snippet.title: Meal Escape in development
snippet.description:
This is Meal Escape, our next idea in development. 

Meal Escape is a survival/platformer/runner game for computers and switch.

Share it to make it playable!!

You can view more stuff of Meal Escape, following it and supporting it, on these project sites:

Game Jolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/mealescape/304532
Itch.io: https://cosmitogames.itch.io/mealescape
Yunoia: https://www.yunoia.com/b/meal-escape
Unity Connect: https://connect.unity.com/p/meal-escape-1
Cartrdge: https://cartrdge.com/cosmitogames/projects/meal-escape

Press Kit: http://www.cosmitogames.com/meal-escape/press/

--
